34:36.491 --> 34:38.951
This story is all about you, Masha.

34:40.995 --> 34:42.163
Protecting you.

34:43.414 --> 34:46.000
And then protecting your daughter.

34:48.669 --> 34:49.504
Okay.

34:50.838 --> 34:52.215
Now we have the why.

34:55.843 --> 34:57.220
Now I want the who.

34:58.721 --> 34:59.847
Who is he?

35:01.057 --> 35:02.725
Who became Reddington?

35:02.809 --> 35:04.268
And where have you gone?

35:07.105 --> 35:10.650
You're my mother,
but you let someone else watch over me,

35:10.733 --> 35:13.736
let me believe you were dead,
but you're living.

